<item>
            <title>[JOHNZON-94] JsonStringImpl and friends are not Serializable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JOHNZON-94</link>
                <project id="12315523" key="JOHNZON">Johnzon</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;JsonStringImpl and friends are not serializable, and it looks like they easily could be.&lt;br/&gt;
This is an issue because in some parts of my application I stick a JsonObject into the session, I can work around it by storing the native types instead, but it seems like these types should be able to serialize since they are wrappers around Java primitives.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;TomEE-7.0.2-SNAPSHOT&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
